OL,3,CWoman charged with manslaughter over
OL,4,C1978 death of child
OL,6,FA 66-year-old woman has been charged
OL,7,Fwith manslaughter over the death of a
OL,8,Fchild in 1978.
OL,10,FFive-year-old Andrea Bernard went to
OL,11,Fhospital after she was assaulted in
OL,12,FAshley Road, Thornton Heath, on June 6
OL,13,F1978, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,15,FShe was treated at a hospital in
OL,16,FCroydon before being transferred to a
OL,17,Fspecialist burns unit in East
OL,18,FGrinstead, Sussex, but died from her
OL,19,Finjuries on July 13 that year.
