OL,6,FThe force launched an investigation
OL,7,Finto her death in September 2022 and,
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, Janice Nix, 66, of
OL,9,FRodenhurst Road, Clapham, south west
OL,10,FLondon was charged with manslaughter.
OL,12,FShe is also accused of cruelty to
OL,13,Fanother child who was aged eight at
OL,14,Fthe time.
OL,16,FNix will appear at Uxbridge
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday.
